    • Field Detail

      • padOnClose

        public boolean padOnClose
        If true, when this stream is closed using its close() method, any unprocessed data will be padded and then encrypted. If false, when this stream is closed any unprocessed data will be discarded.

    • Constructor Detail

      • SHE.EncryptedOutputStream

        public SHE.EncryptedOutputStream(java.io.OutputStream out,
                         SHE cipher)
        Constructs an EncryptedOutputStream from an OutputStream and a Cipher. Note: if the specified output stream or cipher is null, a NullPointerException may be thrown later when they are used.
        Parameters:
        out - the OutputStream object
        cipher - an initialized Cipher object
